    <string name="privacy_policy" translatable="false">
        <![CDATA[
     Bus Timing is a project developed by Gopalakrishnan. This app collects minimal user data, including email addresses for authentication and usernames for personalization. Bus search history and user preferences such as theme, language, and district selection are stored locally to enhance the user experience. The app does not collect location data, payment details, or real-time tracking information.

All user data is securely stored using Firebase Authentication and Firestore, while bus timing details are also maintained in a local Room Database. No personal information is shared with third parties. Users have control over their data and can delete their search history from the app settings. If an account deletion is required, users can request it via email.

For any questions or concerns, please contact gopalkrishnanto@email.com
        ]]>
    </string>

